h1.hidden-phone Check, Check It

p The easiest way to create and use a checklist

h3 Make a new checklist

p A checklist is just a text document. Start new items with a dash (<code>-</code>).

form(action='/list/new', method='POST')
  label Name
    br
    input(type='text', name='name')

  label List Items
    br
    textarea(name='list', id='list', rows='10', cols='80')

  br

  button.button(type='submit') Start
